# =============================================================================
# CLOUDFLARE PAGES ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# =============================================================================
# The newsletter signup functionality uses Cloudflare Pages Functions
# (serverless functions) to securely handle Resend API integration.
#
# These variables should be configured in your Cloudflare Pages dashboard:
# Navigate to: Pages Project > Settings > Environment Variables
#
# Required Variables for Newsletter Function:
# ┌─────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Variable Name       │ Value                                              │
# ├─────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
# │ RESEND_API_KEY      │ Your Resend API key (starts with re_)             │
# │ RESEND_AUDIENCE_ID  │ e5d251bf-2af8-4682-a665-429ff1804e17              │
# └─────────────────────┴────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
#
# SECURITY WARNING:
# - DO NOT add these to .env.local or commit them to the repository
# - These are server-side only variables used by Cloudflare Pages Functions
# - The API key should NEVER be exposed to client-side code
# - Configure them in Cloudflare dashboard, then redeploy your site
#
# For local testing with Wrangler:
# npx wrangler pages dev out \
#   --binding RESEND_API_KEY=re_your_test_key \
#   --binding RESEND_AUDIENCE_ID=e5d251bf-2af8-4682-a665-429ff1804e17
# =============================================================================

